<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Transport Guide | TaiwanMe</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="/image/logo.png" type="image/png">
    
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+TC:wght@400;700&family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@300;400&family=Lato:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
    
    <style>
        /* --- Transport 頁面專屬 CSS --- */

        /* 1. Banner 設定 */
        .transport-banner {
            width: 100%;
            /* 維持 1344 / 768 的比例 */
            aspect-ratio: 1344 / 768; 
            /* 注意：補上斜線 */
            background-image: url('/image/transport/banner.png'); 
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        /* 2. 頁面標題 */
        .page-main-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #5d5d5d;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        .page-subtitle {
            text-align: center;
            color: #888;
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* 3. 文章列表容器 (Grid Layout) */
        .transport-container {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 0 auto 80px;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .transport-grid {
            display: grid;
            /* 電腦版自動調整：每欄最小 320px，放不下就自動換行 */
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
            gap: 40px;
        }

        /* 4. 單篇文章卡片 (仿 Japan Travel 風格) */
        .transport-card {
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            text-decoration: none; /* 連結樣式移除底線 */
            color: inherit;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            border: 1px solid #eee;
        }

        .transport-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        .tp-img-wrapper {
            width: 100%;
            height: 220px;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }

        .tp-img-wrapper img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: transform 0.5s ease;
        }

        .transport-card:hover .tp-img-wrapper img {
            transform: scale(1.05); /* Hover 時圖片微放大 */
        }

        .tp-content {
            padding: 25px;
            flex-grow: 1; /* 確保內容高度對齊 */
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

        .tp-tag {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--accent-color);
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .tp-title {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            color: #333;
            font-family: 'Lato', 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.3;
        }

        .tp-desc {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            flex-grow: 1;
        }

        .read-more-link {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 5px;
        }
        .read-more-link::after {
            content: '→';
            transition: margin-left 0.3s;
        }
        .transport-card:hover .read-more-link::after {
            margin-left: 10px;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <div class="transport-banner"></div>

    <h1 class="page-main-title">Getting Around Taiwan</h1>
    <p class="page-subtitle">From international arrivals to local commuting, here is your complete guide to navigating Taiwan's efficient transportation system.</p>

    <section class="transport-container">
        <div class="transport-grid">

            <a href="#" class="transport-card">
                <div class="tp-img-wrapper">
                    <img src="https://placehold.co/600x400/eee/333?text=Taoyuan+Airport" alt="Taoyuan Airport">
                </div>
                <div class="tp-content">
                    <span class="tp-tag">AIRPORT</span>
                    <h3 class="tp-title">From Taoyuan Airport (TPE) to Cities</h3>
                    <p class="tp-desc">The main gateway to Taiwan. Learn how to get to Taipei, Taichung, and other major cities via Airport MRT, HSR shuttle, and buses.</p>
                    <span class="read-more-link">Read More</span>
                </div>
            </a>

            <a href="#" class="transport-card">
                <div class="tp-img-wrapper">
                    <img src="https://placehold.co/600x400/eee/333?text=Kaohsiung+Airport" alt="Kaohsiung Airport">
                </div>
                <div class="tp-content">
                    <span class="tp-tag">AIRPORT</span>
                    <h3 class="tp-title">From Kaohsiung Airport (KHH) to Cities</h3>
                    <p class="tp-desc">Arriving in the South? Discover the quickest ways to connect from KHH to downtown Kaohsiung, Tainan, and Kenting.</p>
                    <span class="read-more-link">Read More</span>
                </div>
            </a>

            <a href="#" class="transport-card">
                <div class="tp-img-wrapper">
                    <img src="https://placehold.co/600x400/eee/333?text=Other+Airports" alt="Regional Airports">
                </div>
                <div class="tp-content">
                    <span class="tp-tag">AIRPORT</span>
                    <h3 class="tp-title">Regional Airports (TSA, RMQ, & Others)</h3>
                    <p class="tp-desc">Guides for Taipei Songshan (TSA), Taichung (RMQ), and Hualien airports for domestic and regional flights.</p>
                    <span class="read-more-link">Read More</span>
                </div>
            </a>

            <a href="#" class="transport-card">
                <div class="tp-img-wrapper">
                    <img src="https://placehold.co/600x400/eee/333?text=IC+Cards" alt="Payment Methods">
                </div>
                <div class="tp-content">
                    <span class="tp-tag">ESSENTIALS</span>
                    <h3 class="tp-title">Smart Payment: EasyCard & iPASS</h3>
                    <p class="tp-desc">The "Must-Have" item for Taiwan travel. How to buy, top-up, and use these cards for MRT, buses, and convenience stores.</p>
                    <span class="read-more-link">Read More</span>
                </div>
            </a>

            <a href="#" class="transport-card">
                <div class="tp-img-wrapper">
                    <img src="https://placehold.co/600x400/eee/333?text=HSR" alt="Taiwan High Speed Rail">
                </div>
                <div class="tp-content">
                    <span class="tp-tag">INTER-CITY</span>
                    <h3 class="tp-title">Taiwan High Speed Rail (THSR)</h3>
                    <p class="tp-desc">The fastest way to travel along the West Coast. Tips on booking early bird tickets, rail passes, and station guides.</p>
                    <span class="read-more-link">Read More</span>
                </div>
            </a>

            <a href="#" class="transport-card">
                <div class="tp-img-wrapper">
                    <img src="https://placehold.co/600x400/eee/333?text=TRA+Train" alt="Taiwan Railways">
                </div>
                <div class="tp-content">
                    <span class="tp-tag">ISLAND-WIDE</span>
                    <h3 class="tp-title">Taiwan Railways (TRA) Guide</h3>
                    <p class="tp-desc">Perfect for round-island trips and accessing the East Coast (Hualien, Taitung). Understanding train types and booking.</p>
                    <span class="read-more-link">Read More</span>
                </div>
            </a>

            <a href="#" class="transport-card">
                <div class="tp-img-wrapper">
                    <img src="https://placehold.co/600x400/eee/333?text=MRT+Map" alt="MRT Systems">
                </div>
                <div class="tp-content">
                    <span class="tp-tag">URBAN</span>
                    <h3 class="tp-title">Metro Systems (MRT) Guide</h3>
                    <p class="tp-desc">Navigating the subway systems in Taipei, Taoyuan, Taichung, and Kaohsiung. Maps, pricing, and etiquette.</p>
                    <span class="read-more-link">Read More</span>
                </div>
            </a>

            <a href="#" class="transport-card">
                <div class="tp-img-wrapper">
                    <img src="https://placehold.co/600x400/eee/333?text=YouBike" alt="Short Distance Travel">
                </div>
                <div class="tp-content">
                    <span class="tp-tag">LOCAL</span>
                    <h3 class="tp-title">Getting Around the City</h3>
                    <p class="tp-desc">Short-distance options: Renting a YouBike, taking city buses, and using Uber or local Taxis.</p>
                    <span class="read-more-link">Read More</span>
                </div>
            </a>

            <a href="#" class="transport-card">
                <div class="tp-img-wrapper">
                    <img src="https://placehold.co/600x400/eee/333?text=Ferry" alt="Offshore Islands">
                </div>
                <div class="tp-content">
                    <span class="tp-tag">ADVENTURE</span>
                    <h3 class="tp-title">Traveling to Offshore Islands</h3>
                    <p class="tp-desc">Flights and ferries to Penghu, Kinmen, Matsu, Green Island, and Lanyu. Seasonal tips and booking info.</p>
                    <span class="read-more-link">Read More</span>
                </div>
            </a>

            <a href="#" class="transport-card">
                <div class="tp-img-wrapper">
                    <img src="https://placehold.co/600x400/eee/333?text=Lockers" alt="Luggage Storage">
                </div>
                <div class="tp-content">
                    <span class="tp-tag">TIPS</span>
                    <h3 class="tp-title">Luggage Storage & Logistics</h3>
                    <p class="tp-desc">Where to store your bags at stations, airports, and city lockers so you can travel light and hands-free.</p>
                    <span class="read-more-link">Read More</span>
                </div>
            </a>

        </div>
    </section>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>

</body>
</html>